description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 63, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 126, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Box for East, Nine Lives for South, and Box for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50632-64942-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [126 Votes, Top 15% Score]
